snippet.title: Traps in Space
snippet.description:
TRAPS IN SPACE is a brand new puzzle game for the whole family.

Download the game now on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.romainimberti.trapsinspace

Help the little astronaut save the world!

- An addicting and challenging game
- Simple one-finger control
- More than 50 levels
- Mental experience
- Different locations and characters
